east Beirut.
   C. The unconditional withdrawal of all the Israeli forces and
their allies from south Lebanon.
   D. The reconstruction of south Lebanon and Beirut, which have
been devastated by the American-Israeli plot and compensation for
our oppressed people in Lebanon for all the losses it suffered.
   The Islamic Jihad Organization.
